{"tid":490673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2018平昌冬季奧運  IOC：俄羅斯全隊禁賽","createTime":"2017-12-05T23:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T00:37:05.000Z","uid":148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"47cb8d15d82a96dbad18f77a6a4f615d8a34eb40","tid":490673,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T23:42:15.000Z","msg":"IOC(International Olympic Committee，國際奧林匹克委員會)主席巴赫（Thomas Bach）今天在洛桑舉行的紀律委員會後宣布，明年2月9日南韓平昌冬季奧運，將不允許俄羅斯以國家隊報名參賽，但允許未涉及禁藥的運動員，以個人名義「獨立參賽」，屆時若取得獎牌，將不懸掛俄羅斯國旗，也不會演奏國歌，僅以IOC會旗、會歌代替。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯是上屆冬季奧運主辦國，被爆發國家主導選手使用禁藥，並利用主辦國之便，偷換禁藥樣本，躲過禁藥檢查，IOC認為這次國家支持的集體禁藥作弊行為，因此決定明年冬季奧運，將俄羅斯全隊禁賽。(陳國偉／綜合報導)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171206/1254111/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171206%2F1254111%2F&d=3%2F5YkPlJbG%2BQjCW%2B8PjjmbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=9a0dedff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171206%2F1254111%2F&h=7e7305dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171206/1254111/</a>"},{"pid":"b3ba3d4490b70f112dbc2cb5a7aab861e74d8392","tid":490673,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T23:43:26.000Z","msg":"有得獨立參賽都好<br />\n如果戰鬥民族無得出賽 花式溜冰就得返男單有睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fe275306af63a94a66a746b99d2be3498889b4","tid":490673,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:02:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾國"},{"pid":"c5d4f5b0c768e9f0de8ff75f9c378a7de53067e2","tid":490673,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}